	<p class="bodyTitle">
		Medicaid and CHIP in American Samoa
	</p>
	<div class="blueBox">
		<p class="bodyText">
			Medicaid which includes the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP) provides health and long-term care coverage to some people with limited income, including children and parents, pregnant women, people with disabilities, and seniors.
		</p>
	</div>
